reviewText: This video is a must have for any Toad the Wet Sprocket, Glen Phillips, or Lapdog fans.  Although the most easily recognisable song on this video is "All I Want", this video also contains earlier Toad videos such as "Is it For Me?" and "Come Back Down", and more.  Definately worth picking up.

For all the Toad fans I strongly recommend this video. Like watching through a window and seeing the youthful early years of the band and their  progression and development. Plus it may not always be available.
